    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/80977c923ea6ecc7e74f021b93dea139.poster.avif?t=1771893846\" width=650 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/80977c923ea6ecc7e74f021b93dea139.webm?t=1771893846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/80977c923ea6ecc7e74f021b93dea139.mp4?t=1771893846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>普通的捉宠游戏？不，这是一场脑洞大开的神奇萌宠进化之旅！</strong>你的目标只有一个：收集并培养出地表（或是空中）最强的波波，在全球锦标赛中碾压对手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/7e418177849afbebd97dd4593487db8f.poster.avif?t=1771893846\" width=650 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/7e418177849afbebd97dd4593487db8f.webm?t=1771893846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/7e418177849afbebd97dd4593487db8f.mp4?t=1771893846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级才能进化？时代变了，快试试融合基因、培育最强波波！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>从基因开始培育：</strong>将各类波波的基因重组，创造数千种不同外观和属性的全新波波！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超乎想象的进化：</strong>陪伴你的波波从幼苗期一路成长，直至终极进化，成为全新物种！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独一无二的啵啵：</strong>每只波波都有自己的性格和情绪，内卷还是摆烂？看你如何培养！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不但要强更要美：</strong>收集海量时装和配饰，装扮你的波波，做最靓（或最抽象）的崽！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/1e6ac9b2fa7500442620806b104cc853.poster.avif?t=1771893846\" width=650 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/1e6ac9b2fa7500442620806b104cc853.webm?t=1771893846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/1e6ac9b2fa7500442620806b104cc853.mp4?t=1771893846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >养波千日、用波一时，参加锦标赛，验证训练成果！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全能挑战：</strong>无论你的波波是擅长奔跑还是跳跃，都有专属项目和赛事供你挑战！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>团队接力：</strong>培养出了一群优秀的波波？快来组建你的全明星战队，报名团队接力赛！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>传奇波波：</strong>赛场上有几位常胜波波，尝试击败它们、赢取稀有幼苗，培育你的传奇波波！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/f9106ae4d6129f077a80076981ba9a4b.poster.avif?t=1771893846\" width=650 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/f9106ae4d6129f077a80076981ba9a4b.webm?t=1771893846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110830/extras/f9106ae4d6129f077a80076981ba9a4b.mp4?t=1771893846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >训练不是生活的全部，别忘了逛逛星灵岛~</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>买买买：</strong>用锦标赛赚取的奖金来商店街尽情扫货，零食、服装、配饰应有尽有。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时间管理大师：</strong>自由规划你的行程，部分赛事和稀有商品只在特定时段出现，不要错过哦~</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>惊喜彩蛋：</strong>在不同时间段尽情探索星灵岛，总有惊喜（和惊吓）在等着你！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B站：@波波萌宠大作战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小黑盒：@波波萌宠大作战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【加入愿望单，和你的波波开始奇妙的进化之旅吧！】</strong></p>",
